Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: James Munroe's declaration of independence
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydv01
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 7 Apr 1989
The journalism of James "Scottie" Reston, and President Munroe's declaration that America should not be considered as a future target for colonisation by European nations.